            "title": "世衛組織稱全球變暖在降低勞動者的生產力 健康風險也在上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"世衛組織稱全球變暖在降低勞動者的生產力 健康風險也在上升\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ps_zmffUOFOiSdd4W6SSqg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/5dad4be0-7f43-11f0-89fb-c2be4e8ed491\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">世衛組織稱全球變暖在降低勞動者的生產力 健康風險也在上升</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
